<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 12:25:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>贸易机构负责人表示，台湾企业将供应链从中国转移到印度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-firms-shift-supply-chains-india-china-trade-body-chief-says-2024-07-16/</link><description>台湾主要贸易机构负责人告诉路透社，随着主要经济体之间的全球贸易紧张局势加剧，台北和新德里加强了经济联系，台湾企业正在将供应链从中国转移到印度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:55:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-firms-shift-supply-chains-india-china-trade-body-chief-says-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，普华永道考虑将中国金融服务审计人员减半</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pwc-weighs-halving-china-financial-services-audit-staff-say-sources-2024-07-16/</link><description>两名知情人士表示，普华永道 (PwC) 正在考虑将其在中国的金融服务审计人员裁减至多一半，原因是监管调查和客户流失使业务前景黯淡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pwc-weighs-halving-china-financial-services-audit-staff-say-sources-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：鲍威尔激发利率希望，特朗普贸易降温</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-16/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国国有券商将扩大在东南亚的投资银行业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-state-owned-brokerage-ramp-up-investment-banking-business-southeast-asia-2024-07-16/</link><description>国有券商中国银河证券 (CGS) 的一名高级管理人员表示，计划明年将其在东南亚的投资银行团队从目前的 30 人扩大到 50 人，并押注在市场低迷的情况下该地区的交易量会增加在家里。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 08:09:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-state-owned-brokerage-ramp-up-investment-banking-business-southeast-asia-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行成立新的以气候为重点的基础设施融资部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/hsbc-launches-new-climate-focused-infrastructure-finance-unit-2024-07-16/</link><description>一位高级银行高管告诉路透社，英国汇丰银行已成立一个新部门，以挖掘与世界向低碳经济转型相关的基础设施融资和项目融资交易，并聘请了一位前英国政治家来领导该部门。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 08:04:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/hsbc-launches-new-climate-focused-infrastructure-finance-unit-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>鉴于“致命四方”的威胁，英国将增强武装力量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-boost-armed-forces-given-threat-deadly-quartet-2024-07-16/</link><description>英国表示，将加强其“空心化”的武装部队，以确保该国做好准备面对由中国、伊朗、朝鲜和俄罗斯组成的防务审查负责人所说的“致命四方”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 07:49:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-boost-armed-forces-given-threat-deadly-quartet-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚 ADE 预计新飞机短缺导致飞机维修激增</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/malaysias-ade-sees-boom-aircraft-repairs-amid-new-plane-shortages-2024-07-16/</link><description>马来西亚航空服务公司亚洲数字工程 (ADE) 首席执行官马赫什·库马尔 (Mahesh Kumar) 表示，由于新飞机短缺，航空公司将延长飞机的飞行时间，全球飞机维修行业将在未来六年出现更大增长。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 07:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/malaysias-ade-sees-boom-aircraft-repairs-amid-new-plane-shortages-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>美银表示，投资者持乐观态度，但对地缘政治持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/investors-stay-bullish-july-fuelled-by-fed-rate-outlook-2024-07-16/</link><description>美国银行周二的全球基金经理调查显示，对美国利率将下降、防止经济硬着陆的预期使投资者保持看涨情绪，尽管地缘政治构成了这种情况的最大风险。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 06:53:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/investors-stay-bullish-july-fuelled-by-fed-rate-outlook-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>对于全球投资者来说，中国是一个缓慢燃烧的贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/global-investors-china-is-slow-burning-trade-2024-07-16/</link><description>对于在中国股市持有资金的全球投资者来说，最新的经济数据并没有带来任何安慰，只是提醒他们，他们所押注的复苏需要一段时间才能实现。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 06:31:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/global-investors-china-is-slow-burning-trade-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国需求疲软损害了奢侈品公司历峰集团的销售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-says-quarterly-sales-up-1-constant-exchange-rates-2024-07-16/</link><description>卡地亚母公司历峰集团周二表示，截至 6 月份的三个月内，该奢侈品集团的销售额几乎持平，中国需求下滑导致整体业绩略低于预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:47:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-says-quarterly-sales-up-1-constant-exchange-rates-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>ASML订单量预计将因AI芯片热潮而猛增</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmls-order-book-expected-benefit-ai-chip-boom-2024-07-16/</link><description>计算机芯片制造商的顶级设备供应商 ASML 预计将在其新老板周三公布第二季度业绩时报告新订单大量涌入，因为客户扩大产能以满足人工智能芯片蓬勃发展的需求。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:06:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmls-order-book-expected-benefit-ai-chip-boom-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国平安通过可转换债券交易筹集 35 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-ping-an-raises-35-bln-convertible-bond-deal-2024-07-16/</link><description>中国平安保险周二表示，已通过发行可转换债券筹集了 35 亿美元资金。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:03:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-ping-an-raises-35-bln-convertible-bond-deal-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国力图一石激起千层浪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-tries-hit-more-birds-with-one-stone-property-rescue-push-2024-07-16/</link><description>在北京命令中国城市购买新竣工的公寓并将其转变为经济适用房后，他们采取的首要措施是公布扩大补贴资格的计划，并解决这一过程中的其他经济难题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 04:07:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-tries-hit-more-birds-with-one-stone-property-rescue-push-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>暴风雨继续袭击中国，小镇遭遇全年降雨量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beijing-shuts-train-lines-rain-arrives-chinas-north-2024-07-16/</link><description>随着今年夏天袭击南方的极端风暴转移到中部和北部省份，中国河南的一个小镇一天遭遇了近一年的降雨量。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 02:49:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beijing-shuts-train-lines-rain-arrives-chinas-north-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>“特朗普贸易”损害其他资产，美元和美国期货上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-16/</link><description>全球股市周二下跌，投资者思考唐纳德·特朗普的胜利对世界其他地区意味着什么，而日元兑美元走强则下跌，促使日本官员在上周疑似干预后发出更多警告。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 02:24:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>